    {
      "id": "973695c1-5ab4-4b84-9ae0-5b0ee2778983",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Automated early prediction is important in large courses. Thus, authors propose a model that, using data from the first 3 weeks of a course, predict final exam scores - SVM. Data is collected on the first term and the model is deployed on the second term. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "973695c1-5ab4-4b84-9ae0-5b0ee2778983",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
