    {
      "id": "7f345efc-6117-4a11-96f1-ac1b67a93640",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Modelling approach was used in 5 different Computer Science courses across 2 different institutions and taught by 3 different instructors. Predictive performance is competitive with state of the art techniques while having some strenghts:",
